        <item>
            <title>Version 0.7.4</title>
            <sparkle:version>20</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.7.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixes fast Telegram sends that could incorrectly fall back to the “copy text” prompt even though the selected composer accepted the paste.</li>
                    <li>Adds Escape cancellation while a dictation is still being delivered, with a short undo option for accidental cancellation.</li>
                    <li>Keeps the accepted clipboard safety, feedback, required sign-in, and automatic-update defaults enabled for friend builds.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 19:23:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure
