        <item>
            <title>Version 0.7.2</title>
            <sparkle:version>18</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.7.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Improves context-aware capitalization and spacing in ChatGPT/Codex after a clean launch by keeping its editor context available through read-only Accessibility queries.</li>
                    <li>Makes sentence-boundary spacing part of the paste payload, avoiding a delayed trailing Space and improving insertion reliability.</li>
                    <li>Hardens account-scoped History, feedback recording lifecycle, and release provenance.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 20:32:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure
