            <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.5.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Adds a polished first-install DMG with the DictationApp icon and an Applications shortcut.</li>
                    <li>Separates friend authentication from development builds, preventing repeated Keychain password prompts.</li>
                    <li>Requires one normal browser sign-in after installation; future Sparkle updates preserve the friend session.</li>
                </ul>
